dfischer.proxysniffer

Class HttpContentTest

  • java.lang.Object
    • dfischer.proxysniffer.HttpContentTest

  • public class HttpContentTest
extends java.lang.Object
    Content test definition for checking the content of HTTP responses (inclusive HTTP status code and MIME type)
